#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Changelog
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1.0.1: Correct cyclic DCN misassignment for iso-octane/diethyl ether rows 425-427.
# 1.0.0: Initial release; cpnt_vol_* are volume fractions from molar fractions via Cheetah density_ntp (ideal mixing).
#
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Information
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Source: dcn_training_data.dat (InChI components, molar fractions, experimental DCN).
# Components encoded as SELFIES via RDKit InChI -> SMILES -> SELFIES.
# Volume fractions: phi_i = (x_i M_i / rho_i) / sum_j(x_j M_j / rho_j); M in g/mol; rho = density_ntp (kg/m^3).
# Density lookup: cheetah_materials.dat + cheetah_thermophysical.dat (+ cheetah_chemical_identifier.dat).
# Rows written: 448; rows skipped (missing density): 30.
# Skipped components: see dcn_training_data_missing_density.txt.
# Output: data_extractors/leenhouts_fuel_2025/leenhouts_2025_test_dataset_for_model.dat
# Source file SHA-256:
